  <brief_title>Observational Study on the Prophylactic Use of Curosurf in Neonatal Respiratory Distress Syndrome (RDS)</brief_title>
  <official_title>Observational Study in Neonatal Intensive Care Units (NICU) on the Real Life Use of Curosurf in Prophylaxis of RDS in Premature Babies.</official_title>
  <sponsors>
